---
description: UI and UX rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Design style:

- Clean
- Ocean/surf inspired
- Mobile-first
- Fast to demo
- Big readable cards
- Avoid clutter

Important UI components:

- Surf score badge
- Forecast vs Reality card
- Beach trust score
- Report condition buttons
- Favorite beach insight
- Personal analytics cards

Report buttons:

- Waves were there
- No waves
- Smaller than predicted
- Too windy
- Too crowded
- Unsafe
- Perfect session

Dashboard should immediately show:

1. Best beach today
2. Forecast confidence
3. Favorite beach
4. Recent surfer reports

Use plain language:

- Good: "Was it worth going?"
- Bad: "Forecast validation metric"
